## ğŸ“¡ API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint       | Description                          |
|--------|----------------|--------------------------------------|
| GET    | `/games`       | List all stored games                |
| POST   | `/games`       | Add a custom game                    |
| GET    | `/search`      | Search RAWG API (no DB storage)      |
| POST   | `/import`      | Import games from RAWG into database |

